fenton said he will have 45 days to open the center at the 
fourstory 100room former sheraton inn after he signs a federal 
contract which has been mailed to him 
under fentons proposal the halfway house would hold up to 50 
nonviolent prisoners butler county would be paid a fee for each 
prisoner 
