blind is in the early stages of development but still needs 
refinements 
the robot which also uses ultrasound could now guide a blind 
person along an uncluttered street but would have trouble 
separating individual objects or people in crowded areas brady 
said 
currently robots arent as smart as a yearold sheep he 
lamented 
